### 정상 흐름 - 주문 성공
POST {{orderHost}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "BOOK-1",
  "quantity": 1,
  "amount": 15000
}

### 글로벌(Redis) RateLimiter 적용된 진입점
POST {{orderHost}}/orders/global
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "BOOK-1",
  "quantity": 1,
  "amount": 15000
}

### payment - 지연 5초 주입 (TimeLimiter 검증용)
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/delay?ms=5000

### payment - 지연 0으로 복구
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/delay?ms=0

### payment - 실패 주입 (CircuitBreaker OPEN 검증용)
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/fail?fail=true

### payment - 실패 복구
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/fail?fail=false

### inventory - 지연 6초 주입 (Bulkhead 검증용)
POST {{inventoryHost}}/admin/fault/delay?ms=6000

### inventory - 지연 0으로 복구
POST {{inventoryHost}}/admin/fault/delay?ms=0

### inventory - 실패 주입
POST {{inventoryHost}}/admin/fault/fail?fail=true

### inventory - 실패 복구
POST {{inventoryHost}}/admin/fault/fail?fail=false

### [TL-1] payment 지연 5초 주입
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/delay?ms=5000

### [TL-2] 주문 호출 → 2초 후 PENDING/FALLBACK 응답
POST {{orderHost}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{ "sku": "BOOK-1", "quantity": 1, "amount": 15000 }

### [TL-3] 복구
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/delay?ms=0

### [CB-1] payment 실패 주입
POST {{paymentHost}}/admin/fault/fail?fail=true

